title: Did Dem Voters Receive ‘Vote for Trump or Else’ Emails Linked to Overseas Servers?
subtitle: The 2020 presidential election was rife with misinformation campaigns aimed at increasing voter distrust.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: Some registered Democratic Party voters in Alaska and Florida received emails U.S. authorities say were part of a foreign disinformation campaign threatening recipients to “Vote for Trump or else!”
